<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.com/2020/8/donguri-kaonashi-spirited-away-piggy-bank-release">「无脸男」存钱罐，硬币没放够还不愿「吃」</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1356860" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/burp.gif" alt="" width="500" height="276" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/burp.gif 500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/burp-360x199.gif 360w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>
